snippet.title: Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka | Thamma | Nora F, Ayushmann K, Rashmika M |Sachin-Jigar, Rashmeet K, Amitabh B
snippet.description:
Presenting "Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka" from "Thamma". Feat. Nora Fatehi, Ayushmann Khurrana and Rashmika Mandanna.

Song Credits 
Featuring: Nora Fatehi, Ayushmann Khurrana and Rashmika Mandanna
Music : Sachin-Jigar 
Singer : Rashmeet Kaur, Jigar Saraiya
Lyrics : Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Programmed & Arranged : Sachin- Jigar, Abhishek Singh, Hrishikesh Gangan, Amrit Sharma @ White Noise Collectives
Backing Vocals : Abhishek Singh, Amrit Sharma
Music Production Head : Romil Ved
Acoustic, Electric Guitars ,Bass & Strokes : Rhythm Shaw
Recording Engineer : Susmeet Rewaskar @ White Noise Collectives
Mixed & Mastered : Eric Pillai @ FSOB
Assistant Mixing Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai
Music Label : T-Series

Maddock Films presents "Thamma"
In Cinemas on 21st October.

#NoraFatehi #Dilbar #Thamma

Cast: Ayushmann Khurrana, Rashmika Mandanna, Paresh Rawal, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Faisal Malik, Rachit Singh
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan, Amar Kaushik
Directed By: Aditya Sarpotdar
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota, Pooja Prem Patheja
Director of Photography: Saurabh Goswami (ISC)
Music / Background Score: Sachin–Jigar
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Costume Designer: Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
Director of Choreography: Vijay A. Ganguly
Publicity Design: Himanshu & Rahul Nanda (H-One)

Lyrics:

Haan, Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyar Na Kiya
Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyar Na Kiya

Na Kiya
Na Kiya, Jisne Pyar Na Kiya
Kya Kiya, Kya Kiya
Kya Kiya, Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Aankhon Ko Aankhon Se Kisi Ki Chaar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Pyaar Saccha Agar Chahiye
Toh Dua Mein Asar Chahiye
Pyaar Saccha Agar Chahiye
Toh Dua Mein Asar Chahiye
Buzdilon Ka Nahi Kaam Yeh
Pyaar Mein Toh Jigar Chahiye

Ishq Hua Par Khulke Izhaar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya
Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Na Kiya
Na Kiya, Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya
Kya Kiya, Kya Kiya
Kya Kiya, Jisne Pyar Na Kiya

snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Semi Finals | Day 4
snippet.description:
24 top teams clash in the Semi Finals of BMSD 2025. 12 from the Upper Bracket and 12 from the Quarter Finals. Split into 3 groups through the official group draw, every match is packed with high-level BGMI esports action, strategy, and intense competition. Who will rise and secure a spot in the Grand Finals?

Don’t miss a moment of the action, tune in live and cheer for your favorite teams as they push the limits Beyond Limits!

Group A
Phoenix Esports
Nebula Esports
Hero Xtreme Godlike
Blitz Esports
iQOO SOUL
iQOO 8BIT
OnePlus Cincinnati Kids
Infinix TrueRippers

Group B
Autobotz Esports
WHITE WALKERS
Madkings
Victores Sumus
Team AX
OnePlus K9 Esports
GENESIS ESPORTS 
FS ESPORTS

Group C
OnePlus Gods Reign
mysterious4 Esports
Vasista Esports
META NINZA
Likitha Esports
myG Los Hermanos
iQOO ORANGUTAN
First Curiosity

Map Rotation:
Match 1: Miramar–GROUP–A vs B
Match 2: Erangel–GROUP–A vs B
Match 3: Miramar–GROUP–B vs C
Match 4: Erangel–GROUP–B vs C
Match 5: Miramar–GROUP–A vs C
Match 6: Erangel–GROUP–A vs C

#BMSD2025 #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA #KRAFTONINDIAESPORTS #BGMI #bgmishowdown #showdown #bgmishowdown2025 #beyondlimits

snippet.title: Lakshmi Panchali (লক্ষ্মী পাঁচালী) | Pousali Banerjee | Sainik Dey | Lokkhi Pujo | Aalo
snippet.description:
ঘরে ঘরে লক্ষ্মীর পাঁচালী পাঠ ছাড়া কোজাগরী লক্ষ্মীপুজো অসম্পূর্ণ। নিষ্ঠা ও ভক্তি সহকারে এই পাঁচালী পাঠে লাভ হয় কাঙ্খিত ফল। শুনে নিন পৌষালি ব্যানার্জীর পাঠে ‘লক্ষ্মী পাঁচালী’, সম্পূর্ণ লিরিক্স সহ, শুধুমাত্র '@aalo’-তে।

Kojagari Lakshmi Puja is incomplete without reading Lakshmi Panchali in every home. With devotion, this reading fulfills devotees’ desires. Listen to the full lyrical version of ‘Lakshmi Panchali’, chanted by Pousali Banerjee, only on .

snippet.title: The Witcher: Season 4 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After the Continent-altering events of Season Three, Geralt, Yennefer, and Ciri find themselves separated by a raging war and countless enemies. As their paths diverge, and their goals sharpen, they stumble on unexpected allies eager to join their journeys. And if they can accept these found families, they just might have a chance at reuniting for good…. The Witcher: Season 4 returns to Netflix October 30th.

Listen to The Witcher: Season 4 soundtrack here - https://netflixmusic.ffm.to/witcher4

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81628138

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

The Witcher: Season 4 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Scattered to fates unknown, Geralt, Yennefer and Ciri traverse the war-torn Continent and its countless enemies in the hope of finding each other again.

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the new trailer for Predator: Badlands. Experience the film only in theaters and IMAX November 7.

Set in the future on a deadly remote planet, “Badlands” follows a young Predator outcast (played by newcomer Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi) who finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Elle Fanning) as he embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. Produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt and Brent O’Connor, “Predator: Badlands” opens exclusively in movie theaters on November 7 in IMAX, Dolby Cinema, RealD (3D), Cinemark XD, 4DX, ScreenX and premium screens everywhere.

हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

snippet.title: Patriot Malayalam Teaser | Mammootty | Mohanlal | Mahesh Narayanan | Anto Joseph
snippet.description:
From Anto Joseph Productions, the banner behind some of the most acclaimed and celebrated films in recent times, and visionary filmmaker Mahesh Narayanan comes the Official Teaser of Patriot.

Featuring an ensemble of legends: Mammootty, Mohanlal, Fahadh Faasil, Kunchacko Boban, Nayanthara, and Revathy.

snippet.title: Jamnapaar Season 2 - Official Trailer | Ritvik Sahore & Srishti Ganguly Rindani | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Jamnapaar Season 2 - Official Trailer 

Starring: Ritvik Sahore, Varun Badola, Vijay Raz, Anubha Fatehpuria, Srishti Ganguly Rindani, Druv Sehgal, Anushka Kaushik
Production House: Sunshine Productions
Produced By: Sudhir Sharma, Seema Sawhney
Executive Producer: Gaurav Arora
Directed By: Prashant Bhagia
Genre: Drama

About Jamnapaar Season 2 - Shanky’s battle for his own identity collides with Jamnapaar’s quest for one. Torn between his father’s morality and his own ambitions, he steps into a new world—enthralling and transformative—that could change both him and Jamnapaar forever.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is India’s leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who’s your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter – Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more

snippet.title: Mahayoddha Rama - Official Trailer | The Epic Battle of Dharma vs Adharma | Releasing 17th Oct 2025
snippet.description:
👉🏻 SUBSCRIBE to Zee Music Company - https://bit.ly/ZeeMusicCo 

Contiloe Pictures presents Mahayoddha Rama, a visually stunning 3D animated feature inspired by the timeless epic Ramayan.
Releasing in cinemas across India on 17th October 2025, distributed by Cinépolis India

Produced by: Abhimanyu Singh and Roopali Singh (Contiloe Pictures)
Directed by: Raizada Rohit Jaising Vaid

Voice Cast:
Kunal Kapoor as Rama
Jimmy Shergill as Lakshman
Mouni Roy as Sita
Gulshan Grover as Raavan

This trailer offers a closer look at the world of *Mahayoddha Rama* its characters, emotions, and the eternal conflict between dharma and adharma.
Blending powerful storytelling with next-generation 3D animation, the film aims to bring the essence of the *Ramayan* to today’s audiences.

From the makers of *State of Siege – 26/11*, *State of Siege – Temple Attack*, *Taj – Divided by Blood*, and *Taj – Reign of Revenge*, Contiloe Pictures continues its journey of creating strong, content-driven cinema.

Mahayoddha Rama releasing in 3D this Diwali, 17th October 2025.

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Full Video | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the full video of “Thangapoovey” from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. A person who recites this Aarti with true devotion is blessed with wealth and prosperity and a good family life. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds.

snippet.title: Kuanra Punei & Gajalaxmi Brata Katha | ଗଜଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ବ୍ରତ ଗାଥା ଓ ପୂଜା ବିଧି | Namita Agrawal
snippet.description:
🌸 Listen to the sacred *Gajalaxmi Brata Katha* (ମା' ଗଜଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ବ୍ରତ କଥା) narrated with devotion by Namita Agrawal, along with the divine folk song *“Kuanra Punei Janha Go Phula Baulabeni”*. This special video brings you the powerful story (କାହାଣୀ) and puja vidhi (ପୂଜା ବିଧି) of Ma Gajalaxmi, observed during Kuanra Punei and Kartika Purnima in Odisha.

📖 Watch this video to understand the spiritual importance of the brata, the rituals to be performed, and the blessings of Goddess Laxmi.

🛕 Content Includes:
- Gajalaxmi Brata Katha (Odia narration)
- Puja Vidhi & Niyama
- Traditional Kuanra Punei song by Namita Agrawal

🎤 Voice & Song: Namita Agrawal  
🎼 Music Label: Sidharth Music  
🎊 Occasion: Kuanra Punei /  Gajalaxmi Puja

Their voices not only defined but exemplified the true meaning of romance in their songs, leaving listeners spellbound and hearts filled with love. Meri Zindagi Ke Malik is a manifestation of the romantic aura of the90ss, captivating listeners in the beautiful melody. 

Meri Zindagi Ke Malik

Let's embark on a beautiful journey with these romantic songs that evoke a thousand emotions, leaving us reminiscing about forgotten love. हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna

Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,

Watan damaan de naal te zaat jogi, sanu saak kabeelrha khesh keha.
Jehra watan te jat wal dhiaan rakhe, duniyaan daar hai oh darvesh keha.


Main ikallrha gall na jaan’na haan, tusi dovein nanaan bharjaaiyan ni.
Malzadiyan waang banaa teri, payi baithi hain suram-salaaiyan ni.
Pair pakkarh fakeer de te de bhikhia, arhiyan kehiyan kawariye laiyan ni.
dhyann rab te rakh , na ho tatti, gusse hon na bhaliyan deeyaan jaaiyan ni.
Tainu shauk hai tinan da bhagparriye, jinnaan daachiyan bahar charaaiyan ni.
Waris Shah ohh sadaa hi jindde ne, jinnaan keetiyaan neik kamaaiyan ni.

Dil fikar ne gheriya band hoya, Ranjha jiu gotey lakh khai baitha.
Sathon hoonj dhuaan sir cha turia, kaale bagh vich dher machai baitha.
Akhiyan meet ke rab dhiaan dhar ke, chare taraf hai dhunrha laai baitha.
Waris Shah us waqt nu jhoorda ee, jis velrhe akhiyaan laai baitha.

Heer naike patt da pahin tewar, waali itar faleel malanwaudi hai.
Kanjal bhinne neinn apraadh lathe, dovey husan de kattak le dhaanwdi hai.
Ranjha vekh ke aakhda pari koi, ikke bhawein taan Heer siyaal hove.
Koi hoor ki mohni indraani, Heer hove taan saiyan de naal howe.
Waris Shah aayi chambrhi Ranjhane nu, jeha gadhe de gaale vich laal hoye.


Awull pairr pakkrhe itaqaak karke, fer naal kalejhe de lag gayi.
Nawan taor ajube da nazar aaya, vekho jal patang te agg gayi.
Kehi lag gayi chinaga jag gayi, khabar jag gayi vajj dharagh gayi.
Yaaro thaggan di rihuryi Heer jatti, muh lagadiyaan yaar nu thagg gayi.
Agge dhoonwaan dhukhendrha jogirhe da, utton phook ke jhugrhe agg gayi.
Yaar yaar da bagh vich mel hoya, gall aam mashhoor ho jag gayi.
Waris tarutiyan nu rabb melda ae, vekho kamle nu pari lag gayi.


Heer ho rukhsat Ranjhe yaar kolon, aakhe sahitiye mata pakaiye ni.
Mere waaste us ne lae tarale, kiven us di aas pujaiye ni.



Aggon raiba sairfaan boliyan ne, keha bhabiye ni matha kherhiya ee.
Nain shokh hoye rang chamak aaiya, koi jobne da khooh gediyaa ee.
Nain mast gallan teriyan laal hoyiyan, dukkan bhann choli vich teliyaan ni.
Kise hik teri naal hik jodi, pedu naal valoodran meliyan ni.
Teriyaan gallan te dandan de daarah disan, ajj sodhiyaan thakaran cheliyaan ni.
Ajj nahi iyaaliyan khabar ladhi, baghiyaarann ne roliyaan cheliyaan ni.


Parnehan da mainu asar hoya, rang jarad hoya ese waaste ni.
shhapan khubb gayiyan gallan meriyan te, daag laal peye ese waaste ni.
Katte jaande nu bhaj ke mili saan main, tainiyan dhilliyan ne ese waaste ni.
Runni athru dulle san mukhde te, khull gaye tatolrhey paasate ni.
Mudhi payi banere te vekhdi saan, pedu laal hoye ese waaste ni.
Surakhi hothaan di aape mai chuus layi, rang udd gaya ese waaste ni.
Katta ghuttiya vich galvakadi de, dukkan laal hoyiyan ese waaste ni.
Mere pedu nu katte ne thudd maari, laasaan bhakhlan diyan mere mass te ni.
Hor puchh waris main gharibni nu, ki aakhde lok muhasate ni.

snippet.title: आज " शरद पूर्णिमा के दिन चमत्कारी व्रत कथा " सुनने से विष्णु लक्ष्मी सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण करते है
snippet.description:
Sharad Purnima :-
शरद पूर्णिमा हिन्दू पंचांग के अनुसार आश्विन माह की पूर्णिमा तिथि को मनाई जाती है और यह तिथि धार्मिक दृष्टि से बेहद शुभ मानी जाती है। इसे रास पूर्णिमा, कोजागरी पूर्णिमा और चंद्र पूर्णिमा के नाम से भी जाना जाता है।  इस पावन अवसर पर पूजा-पाठ दान-पुण्य और पूर्णिमा कथा सुनने से विशेष फल मिलता है और शरद पूर्णिमा के दिन मां लक्ष्मी सुख, सौभाग्य और धन-वैभव प्रदान करती है

"One In A Million” is the pop anthem of 2025, marking Jordan Sandhu’s bold take on modern pop music. With infectious beats by Avvy Sra and stunning visuals directed by Rupan Bal, the song blends high energy, style, and romance — delivering a catchy vibe that’s impossible to skip. A must-watch for every pop lover, this is Jordan Sandhu like you’ve never seen before!

snippet.title: Kalyug Aavyo - DHUN - Kiran Prajapati - હળહળ તો કળયુગ આવ્યો - Gujrati Bhajan
snippet.description:
Kiran Prajapati Presents...

Kalyug Aavyo - DHUN - Kiran Prajapati - હળહળ તો કળયુગ આવ્યો  


 “Kalyug Aavyo” – આ ભજન માણસના સ્વભાવમાં, પહેરવેશમાં અને જીવનશૈલીમાં આવેલા પરિવર્તનોને સુંદર રીતે રજૂ કરે છે.
પહેલાના સમયમાં માણસ સાધારણ જીવન જીવતો, સરળ પહેરવેશ, સચ્ચાઈ અને પ્રેમથી ભરેલો હોતો.
પણ આજે કલિયુગમાં માણસનો સ્વભાવ બદલાઈ ગયો છે — બહારથી ચમકદાર, અંદરથી ખાલી.

Title:Kalyug Aavyo - DHUN - Kiran Prajapati - હળ હળ તો કળયુગ આવ્યો 
Singer: Kiran Prajapati 
Music: Manoj Vimal 
Mixing: Hardik Sagar
Dhun Mandli: Botad  
Video: Maruti Movies (Shailesh Patel)
Editing: Sanjay Prajapati 
Disign: Kaushal Prajapati 
Light : Nilkanth Light Botad
Lable: Kiran Prajapati

“કલિયુગ આવ્યો” ભજન માનવીના જીવનમાં સમય પ્રમાણે આવેલા ફેરફારોને સ્પર્શે છે — પહેલાના સાદા, સંસ્કારી જીવનથી લઈ આજના ચમકદાર પણ ખાલી જીવન સુધી. એક આધ્યાત્મિક સંદેશ આપતું ગુજરાતી ભજન.

#KalyugAavyo #GujaratiBhajan #Dhun #KiranPrajapatiBhajan #GujaratiSong #DevotionalSong #BhaktiGeet #KalyugReality #KiranPrajapati  #GujaratiMusic #Bhajan #SpiritualSong #GujaratiDevotion #Kirtan #KiranPrajapatiOfficial #KiranPrajapatiNewSong

snippet.title: Shinchan Kinderjoy Scam 😅🍫 Brainrot Kids & RC Car Trouble | Franklin GTA 5 Malayalam Funny Story
snippet.description:
😅🍫 Shinchan Kinderjoy Scam with Brainrot Kids in GTA 5 Malayalam!
Franklin, Shinchan, Doraemon, Franklin’s 5 kids, and an alien kid visit the park. There they meet Brainrot Balerino Capucino and Tung Tung Sahur, struggling with their naughty brainrot kids.

Shinchan tricks them, promises Kinderjoy, and takes money to buy an RC car 😂. The next day, the brainrot kids come to Franklin’s house for Kinderjoy, but Shinchan is missing! While Shinchan is racing his RC car against Chotta Bheem, he falls into the river 🌊. Franklin rescues him and surprises the kids with real Kinderjoys ❤️.

👉 Full of RC car racing, brainrot chaos, and Kinderjoy fun in GTA 5 Malayalam style!

🔥 Watch more GTA 5 Malayalam Funny Videos: [ https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLC2H5ToAT8sRrAZ3E9v78gMduh_p4yto2 ]

snippet.title: Pariyan Vargi | Gulab Sidhu | Nirvair Pannu | Tanu Grewal | SVCW | 10 October | Jass Records
snippet.description:
✨Pariyan Vargi is not just a song — it’s a romantic vibe beautifully expressed in the soulful vocals of Gulab Sidhu. Penned and composed by Dharp, the track tells the story of a boy who imagines a girl as a fairy in his dreams, wondering how she would look if he ever met her in reality. In a poetic way, he says that when she looks into the mirror, even the mirrors would lose themselves in her beauty.

🎬 “Soohe Ve Cheere Waleya” 

🌎 Worldwide Releasing on 10th Oct 2025
🎬 “SOOHE VE CHEERE WALEYA” Movie Releasing in Cinema on  10th Oct

Directed By : Janjot Singh
Written By : Bir Singh 
Produced By : Preet inder Singh , Sunpreet Singh , Harpreet Shahpur , Mickey Sra

Song : Pariyan Vargi
Singer : Gulab Sidhu
Lyrics : Dharp
Music : Jashan Inder
Gulab Sidhu Sync DI : Nirpjeet Sidhu

Introducing : Nirvair Pannu
Starring : Nirvair Pannu , Tanu Grewal , Bir Singh , Hasanpreet kaur, Sukhi Chahal , Jatinder Kaur , Rupinder Rupi ,Baljinder Kaur , Balwinder Bullet , Honey Mattu , Gurinder Makna , Nav Lehal 
D.O.P : Ravi Kumar Sana
Dialogues : Sukhi Dhllon & Bir Singh
Additional Dialogues : Nav Lehal
Music : Beat Minister , Jashan Inder , Deol Harman.
Art Director : Ashok Dulguch

Director of Choreography : Ritchie Burton & Arvind Thakur
Action Director : Monu Kamboj

Associate art director : Baldeep Singh

snippet.description:

महाकाल - महाकाल को भगवान शंकर का दशावतारों में से प्रथम अवतार माना है। इस अवतार में भगवान शिव ने दूषण नामक असुर का वध किया था और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता महाकाली हैं।
तारकेश्वर - तारकेश्वर या तार भगवान शिव का दूसरा अवतार है और इस अवतार की शक्ति तारा देवी हैं। इस अवतार में भगवान शिव ने तारकासुर को उस समय दर्शन दिए थे जब वह शिवपुत्र कार्तिकेय द्वारा परास्त होकर मृत्यु की प्रतीक्षा कर रहा था।
बाल भुवनेश - बाल भुवनेश को शिव का तीसरा अवतार माना जाता है और इस अवतार की शक्ति बाला भुवनेशा हैं।
षोडश विद्येश - षोडश विद्येश को भगवान शंकर का चौथा अवतार माना जाता है और इस अवतार की शक्ति षोडशा विद्येशा माना जाता है।
भैरवनाथ - भैरव या भैरवनाथ को भगवान शिव का पांचवा अवतार माना जाता है। इस अवतार में भगवान शिव ने अंधकासुर नामक दैत्य का वध किया था और इस अवतार की शक्ति भैरवी हैं।
छिन्नमस्तक - छिन्नमस्तक भगवान शिव का छठा अवतार माना जाता है। यह अवतार शीश रहित अवतार है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता छिन्नमस्ता को माना जाता है।
द्युम्वान - द्युम्वान भगवान शंकर का सातवाँ अवतार माना जाता है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता द्युमावती मानी जाती हैं।
बगलामुख - बगलामुख भगवान शिव का आठवाँ अवतार है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता बगलामुखी मानी जाती हैं।
मातंग - मातंग भगवान शंकर का नौवां अवतार है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता मातंगी मानी जाती हैं। इस अवतार में ब्रह्मदेव के सभी गुण मौजूद हैं।
कमल - कमल भगवान शंकर का दसवां और अंतिम अवतार माना जाता है और इस अवतार की शक्ति माता कमला मानी जाती हैं। इस अवतार में भगवान विष्णु के सभी गुण मौजूद हैं।

Lyrics:-

हो नीली पीली चूड़ी ले अईयो कंगना,,
करवाचौथ पे उपासी रहूंगी सजना,,,

हा लंबे लंबे घूंघट को धीरे से उठईयो 
पतले पतले होटन पे लिपस्टिक लगईयो 

हा सोलह सिंगार गोरी करियो जरूर,,
रे गोरी तोड़ के दिखावे अनिल चांद को गुरूर,,

हो बाबुल की गलियों से तेरे घर आई रे
बैठी हु प्यासी शरम तोय न आई रे,,

पानी तेरे हाथ से पिलादे सजना,,
करवाचौथ पे उपासी रहूंगी सजना,,

हा छोटी छोटी बातन पे रूठो न गोरी,,
आवे में हो गई है थोड़ी सी देरी,,

हा सॉरी सॉरी बोलूं मोकु करियों न दूर,,
रे गोरी तोड़ के दिखावे अनिल चांद को गुरूर,,,


Ho nili pili chudi le aiyo Kangna,,
Karwachauth pe upasi rahungi sajna,,

Ha lambe lambe gungate ko dhire se uthaiyo,,
Patale patale hotan pe lipistic lagaiyo,,

Ha solah singar gori kariya jarur,,
Re gori tod ke dikhave Anil Chand ko gurur,

Ho Babul ki galiyon se tere ghar aai re,,
Bhethi hu pyasi sharam toy na aai re,,

Paani tere haath se pilade sajna,,
Karwachauth pe upasi rahungi sajna,,

Ha chhoti chhoti baatan pe rutho na gori,,
Aave me ho gai hai thodi si deri,,

Re sorry sorry bolu moku Kariyo na door,,
Re gori tod ke dikhave Anil Chand ko gurur,,,

'गायत्री' एक छन्द भी है जो ऋग्वेद के सात प्रसिद्ध छंदों में एक है। इन सात छंदों के नाम हैं- गायत्री, उष्णिक्, अनुष्टुप्, बृहती, विराट, त्रिष्टुप् और जगती। गायत्री छन्द में आठ-आठ अक्षरों के तीन चरण होते हैं। ऋग्वेद के मंत्रों में त्रिष्टुप् को छोड़कर सबसे अधिक संख्या गायत्री छंदों की है। गायत्री के तीन पद होते हैं (त्रिपदा वै गायत्री)। अतएव जब छंद या वाक के रूप में सृष्टि के प्रतीक की कल्पना की जाने लगी तब इस विश्व को त्रिपदा गायत्री का स्वरूप माना गया। जब गायत्री के रूप में जीवन की प्रतीकात्मक व्याख्या होने लगी तब गायत्री छंद की बढ़ती हुई महिता के अनुरूप विशेष मंत्र की रचना हुई, जो इस प्रकार है:

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

ॐ भूर् भुवः सुवः ।
तत्सवितुर्वरेण्यं
भर्गो॑ देवस्यधीमहि ।
धियो यो नः प्रचोदयात् ॥
